This is to upgrade to USPS Priority shipping (2 to 3 BUSINESS DAYS). VERY IMPORTANT, Our lead time and production time will not change but the transit time to get to you will be 2 to 3 days.

So remember this only expedites the shipping time not the production time. Don't purchase this without contacting us first.

Note that this is in addition to a shirt purchase, this item cannot be bought alone.
